The '''Sibioara Wind Farm''' is a proposed wind power project in [[Sibioara]], [[Vaslui County]], [[Romania]]. It will have 42 individual [[wind turbine]]s<ref name="micii jucatori">{{cite web|url=http://www.standard.ro/articol_80098/cine_sunt_si_cum_rezista_in_criza_micii_jucatori_din_piata_eolienelor.html|title=Cine sunt si cum rezista in criza micii jucatori din piata eolienelor|date=2009-02-10|work=standard.ro|publisher=Business Standard|language=Romanian|accessdate=2009-03-05}}{{dead link|date=May 2018 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref> with a nominal output of around 1 [[Watt#Megawatt|MW]] which will deliver up to 42 MW of power, enough to power over 26,552 homes, with a capital investment required of approximately US$50 million.

